quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  39,32,"E ko hommbo …ìuri too√±de wa on jeddu…óo …óo e hoore Allah, maa o yeddi goonga kan nde ko arunoo e makko? E wonaa Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde yeddu…ìe …ìeen?"
  39,33,"Oon noon gardu…óo e goonga, o goongini …óuum, ko …ìen ngoni goo≈ã…óu…ìe …ìeen."
  39,34,"Hino woodani kala ko …ìe paaletee, ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe; ko …óuum njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìeen."
  39,35,"fii no Allah yaawtirana …ìe, ko …ìuri bon'de e ko …ìe golli kon, O yo…ìitira …ìe njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndiin, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe ngollaynoo kon."
  39,36,"Allah siforaali yonugol jiyaa…óo makko on? He…ìe kul…ìinire …óin …ói wonaa mo. Kala mo Allah majjini, haray Feewnoowo alanaa mo."
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah feewni, majjinoowo mo alaa. Allah siforaali won'de poolu…óo, Jom lepte?"
  39,38,"Pellet, si a la…ìndike …ìe: "Ko hommbo tagi kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin?", ma …ìe mbi'u: "Ko Allah". Maaku: "Yeewtee kam fii …óin …ói ndewoton ga Allah, si Allah faandanike lam lorra, hara …ói huncanay kam lorra makko kan? Maa si o faandanike lam yurmeende, taw si …ói ha…óay kam yurmeende makko nden? Maaku: "Allah yonii kam, ko e makko hoolnotoo…ìe …ìen tuuginotoo"."
  39,39,"Maaku: "eey mon yim…ìe am, ngollee e laawol mon, min ko e [laawol am] mi ngollirta. Aray ka nganndon."
  39,40,"ko hommbo lepte koynay…óe ngaroyat e muu…óum, lepte duumii…óe njippoo e makko."